AWS DataSync
Simplifies, automates, and accelerates moving data
AWS DataSync simplifies, automates, and accelerates moving and replicating data between
on-premises storage and AWS services over the network.


How it works ?
Deploy an agent
Deploy a DataSync agent and associate it to your AWS account.
Create a task
Create a task by specifying the location of your data source and destination, and any
options you want to use to configure the transfer.
Start the transfer
Start the task and monitor data movement in the console or with Amazon CloudWatch.
